nnual rent for the use of the Subject of the Lease, which shall be calculated as the amount of CZK 10,000,000.00 (in words: ten million Czech crowns), excl. VAT, minus the sum of the annual rents paid by all Further Tenants and all Other Tenants (as specified in Schedule No. 8 hereof) (hereinafter the “Annual Rent”)."}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_18","part":"s1p68","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"2."}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_9","part":"s1p68","offsets":[{"start":3,"text":"The Tenant shall pay the Rent monthly, always in the relevant calendar month to which the given Rent relates"}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_9","part":"s1p68","offsets":[{"start":146,"text":"The Parties agree that the amount of the Monthly Rent for the month of July 2008 shall equal CZK 301,655.00 (in words: three hundred and one thousand six hundred and fifty-five Czech crowns) plus the applicable VAT; the amount of the Monthly Rent for the month of August 2008 shall equal CZK 376,655.00 (in words: three hundred and seventy-six thousand six hundred and fifty-five Czech crowns) plus the applicable VAT; and the amount of the Monthly Rent for each subsequent calendar month (i.e. September 2008 to June 2009) shall equal CZK 455,310.00 (in words: four hundred and fifty-five thousand three hundred and ten Czech crowns) plus the applicable VAT per calendar month. The Tenant shall always pay the Monthly Rent by a transfer to the Landlord’s account No. 6319656084/2700, kept by UniCredit Bank Czech Republic, a.s., branch in Zlín (hereinafter the “Landlord’s Account”). The day when the amount is credited to the Landlord’s Account shall be deemed to be the date of payment of the Monthly Rent. The Tenant shall pay the Monthly Rent on the basis of a tax document issued by the Landlord and within the set period of maturity, where the maturity of the tax document (invoice) shall equal 8 (eight) calendar days from the date of its delivery. The tax document shall contain all the requisites required by the applicable law. The first calendar day of the month in which the Monthly Rent is to be paid shall be the date of taxable supply."}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_18","part":"s1p70","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"3."}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_9","part":"s1p70","offsets":[{"start":3,"text":"The Parties agree that the Tenant shall commence paying the Monthly Rent as of July 1, 2008. The Parties agree that also the first Monthly Rent in the amount of CZK 301,655.00 (in words: three hundred and one thousand six hundred and fifty-five Czech crowns) plus the applicable VAT shall be paid in accordance with Art. IV (2)."}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_18","part":"s1p71","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"4."}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_18","part":"s1p72","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"5."}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_16","part":"s1p74","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"V."}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_15","part":"s1p75","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"Fees for Services Related to Lease"}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"